===Additional Raptor Chess Sets (.98RC6+) ===

As of .98RC6 Raptor supports Jin chess sets as well.

To install a chess set download it, then in Raptor click File->Install chess set.

==All sets: [http://raptor-chess-interface.googlecode.com/files/ChessSet_AllSets.zip ChessSet_AllSets.zip]==
